text: Hello! Anyone have an idea as to why our Google Webmaster Tools and GTM modules suddenly appeared on our edit page view?
<@ULMHFHBGF> Check if the module may have had the `overrideable=False` parameter removed

adding that to the end of the module when you include it should stop that from showing. An example of that would be using:
``` {% module "module_1554502162189222" path="/path/to/module" no_wrapper=True, overrideable=False %}```
